    "# Preprocessing Pipeline\n",
    "\n",
    "See `NN_Project_clean.ipynb` for the complete preprocessing pipeline.\n",
    "\n",
    "Steps:\n",
    "1. Convert MIDI to piano-roll (8 Hz, 128 pitches)\n",
    "2. Binarize piano rolls\n",
    "3. Segment into 64-frame windows\n",
    "4. 80/20 train/validation split\n",
    "5. REMI tokenization for Transformer (vocab=397)\n"
   ]
